			<div class="content" id="post-content-4101820">
									

<p>So, this piece started with me asking myself, &quot;well, Wonder World is a pretty happy place with rainbows and sunshine! What would happen if it rained there?&quot;</p>
<p>And then I followed that train of thought all the way here. Because of course, when all you have is sunshine, that just mean that when it rains, it's going to pour.</p>
<p>I'd like to thank Uncle Nicolini, DrChandra, rumetzen, and Stallmantic for critiquing this.</p>
<p>And don't forget, when faced with those bad bad emotions to just Smile Them Away!</p>

							</div>

								
