			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4102953">
									

<p>Gotta think the Wonder World (TM) mental health service is one of the most draconian, and effective, in the multiverse. They've got a whole lot of weird going on, and have to maintain high standards because all of their products are anomalous and intended for children. Maybe some folks with chronic mental health issues end up leaving Wonder World voluntarily, because even living under the Masquerade is less draining and difficult than maintaining perpetual perkiness while struggling with one's symptoms.</p>

